  <Features
    title="Why Choose Us?"
    items={[
      [
        {
          title: 'Experienced',
          description:
            'This isn’t our first rodeo! Here at QAccounting we have been offering accounting services to businesses up and down the country for over twenty years. Our team of accountants has vast experience and expertise and is on hand to help all of our customers every working day.',
          icon: 'tabler:brand-tailwind',
        },
        {
          title: 'Trusted',
          description:
            'We believe that your relationship with your accountant should be based on trust. We feel that our trust with our customers is reflected in the hundreds of five star reviews left by our happy clients. We’re rated 92% on Reviews.co.uk and strive to offer the best service possible.',
          icon: 'tabler:components',
        },
        {
          title: 'Transparents',
          description:
            'We’ve developed state-of-the-art technology giving our customers visibility and control of their business’ accounts and finances. We also cater to external bookkeeping software such as Xero meaning that we will meet your bookkeeping and software needs.',
          icon: 'tabler:list-check',
        },
      ],
      [
        {
          title: 'Recognised',
          description:
            'Joining QAccounting means that you are joining one of the industry’s leading online accountants, offering recognised, award-winning accounting services to businesses large and small. Our reputation has been well earned over our many years trading.',
          icon: 'tabler:rocket',
        },
        {
          title: 'Tailored',
          description:
            'We offer tailored accouting solutions for you and your business. That’s right! We offer packages you can custom build to suit your needs, making your monthly accounting service cost-effective in that you only pay for the services and products you need.',
          icon: 'tabler:arrows-right-left',
        },
        {
          title: 'Compliant',
          description:
            'In the world of accounting, making sure information is accurate and taxes are submitted on time is the difference between a good accountant and a bad one. We offer a range of industry-leading compliant solutions giving you complete peace of mind when it comes to your taxes.',
          icon: 'tabler:bulb',
        },
      ],
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    title="We're Here to Help"
    subtitle="As accountants with over twenty years of experience, we’ve helped thousands of individuals with their financial affairs. Whether you’re new to accounting or thinking of switching, we have the knowledge and solutions to suit your needs."
  />

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isReversed
    isAfterContent
    image={{
      src: import('~/assets/images/1.png'),
